  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, until about my third year with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think in the year 1941, I married a-- a lady from Washington here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And our marriage went along pretty well until I [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] went overseas, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and then I began to feel that her beliefs and feelings were not sufficiently compatible with mine, [? so ?] that we should continue.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I asked her to get a divorce, which she did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] well, I can't tell you exactly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the year escapes me, but it was about the fourth year or something like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At all events, by-- when I got to Nuremberg, I-- by that time, I was a-- a free man.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I left it in May '42 to enlist in the US Army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't hear you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I knew I would be drafted, and I had wanted to get in earlier.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'd applied for a Navy commission, but I have a left leg that's 3/4 of an inch shorter than my right.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And although this has never stopped me from being in athletics, the Navy noticed it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so, all of a sudden, I find myself, despite some very good recommendations, being turned down.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I decided I'll go the other route, and I went in and enlisted and worked my way up, eventually was discharged as a captain.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "May 1942.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where was I what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because of my background in language and so on, I was shipped to England within three weeks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I expected I was going to be transferred to something where I-- my language ability and my geographic knowledge would be useful.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
